%% Splitnorder - Upload → Stem üretim akışı
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as Kullanıcı
    participant V as JSP View (upload.jsp)
    participant C as UploadController
    participant J as JobService
    participant DAO as JobDao / StemDao (CriteriaBuilder)
    participant DB as MySQL
    participant CI as ColabInferenceService
    participant F as Flask (Demucs)

    U->>V: Ses dosyası + model seç
    V->>C: POST /upload (multipart)
    C->>J: createJob(user, file, model)
    J->>DAO: save(Job: PENDING)
    DAO->>DB: INSERT jobs
    J->>CI: processJobAsync(jobId)
    CI->>F: POST /api/separate (file, model, jobId)
    F-->>CI: 200 OK (stem dosyaları hazır)
    CI->>DAO: save(Stem x4: vocals/drums/bass/other)
    DAO->>DB: INSERT stems
    CI->>DAO: update Job → COMPLETED
    DAO->>DB: UPDATE jobs
    U->>C: GET /job/{id} (polling)
    C-->>V: result.jsp + stem oynatıcı
